[package]
name = "safe_network"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.7.3"
authors = ["MaidSafe Developers <dev@maidsafe.net>"]
description = "The Safe Network Core. API message definitions, routing and nodes, client core api."
homepage = "https://maidsafe.net"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/sn_node"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = []
categories = []
license = "GPL-3.0"
repository = "https://github.com/maidsafe/safe_network"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.40"
async-recursion = "0.3.2"
async-trait = "0.1.42"
base64 = "~0.10.1"
bincode = "1.3.1"
bls_dkg = "~0.5.0"
cookie-factory = "0.3.1"
crdts = "6.3.3"
dashmap = "~4.0.2"
dirs-next = "2.0.0"
ed25519 = "1.0.1"
exponential-backoff = "1.0.0"
futures = "~0.3.13"
futures-util = "~0.3.13"
hex = "~0.3.2"
hex_fmt = "~0.3.0"
itertools = "0.10.0"
lazy_static = "1"
lru = "0.6.5"
multibase = "~0.8.0"
pickledb = "~0.4.0"
qp2p = "~0.12.0"
rand = "~0.7.3"
rand_chacha = "~0.2.2"
rand_core = "~0.5.1"
regex = "1.4.3"
resource_proof = "0.8.0"
rmp-serde = "~0.15.4"
secured_linked_list = "~0.3.0"
self_encryption = "~0.24.1"
serde_bytes = "0.11.5"
serde_json = "1.0.53"
signature = "1.1.10"
sled = "0.34.6"
sn_launch_tool = "~0.2.0"
structopt = "~0.3.17"
thiserror = "1.0.23"
tracing = "~0.1.26"
tracing-appender = "~0.1.2"
tracing-futures = "~0.2.5"
tracing-subscriber = "~0.2.15"
uhttp_uri = "~0.5"
url = "2.2.0"
urlencoding = "1.1.1"
xor_name = "1.1.10"

[dependencies.bls]
version = "2.0.1"
features = []
optional = false
package = "blsttc"

[dependencies.bytes]
version = "1.0.1"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "1.0.0"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.fxhash]
version = "~0.2.1"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.miscreant]
version = "~0.5.2"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.self_update]
version = "~0.16.0"
features = ["rustls", "archive-tar", "archive-zip", "compression-flate2", "compression-zip-deflate"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.111"
features = ["derive", "rc"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tiny-keccak]
version = "2.0.2"
features = ["sha3"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.6.0"
features = ["macros", "fs", "sync", "io-util", "rt", "rt-multi-thread"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
assert_matches = "1.3"
proptest = "0.10.1"
rand_xorshift = "~0.2.0"
structopt = "~0.3.17"
tempdir = "~0.3.7"
yansi = "~0.5.0"

[dev-dependencies.rand]
version = "~0.7.3"
features = ["small_rng"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "~0.6.4"
features = ["time"]
optional = false

[features]
always-joinable = []
chaos = []
default = ["testing"]
testing = []

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "safe_network"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
[profile.release]
incremental = true

skeleton.config_file:
# 64 bit MSVC
[target.x86_64-pc-windows-msvc]
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=/STACK:0x800000"
]

# 64 bit Mingw
[target.x86_64-pc-windows-gnu]
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,--stack,0x800000"
]
